Template: custom-conf-lightdm/display-scale
Type: string
Default: 1
Description: Display scaling factor ?
 Use a greater-than-1 (integer) value to enlarge the greeter display appearance.

Template: custom-conf-lightdm/indicators
Type: multiselect
Choices: power, session, language
Default: power, session, language
Description: Greeter indicators ?
 Please select the indicators to display in the greeter:
 .
  - power:    power actions (reboot, shutdown, etc.)
  - session:  session types
  - language: language selector

